title: [The Vamped Vault]
description: Dusky, autumnal shades of carnelian, gold, and foxfire green pour through stained glass window panes encircling the elongated vault, the blanched stone flooring dappled in the warm tones.  A raised beveled ledge solidly frames the bare walls, adjacent to a finely woven rowan case and a massive cast iron cauldron resting at the center of the space.
